联结表 联结用于在一条 SELECT 语句中关联表，返回一组输出。
1 2 3  SELECTvend_name,prod_name,prod_priceFROMVendors,ProductsWHEREVendors.vend_id=Products.vend_id;  联结多个表：
1 2 3 4 5  SELECTprod_name,vend_name,prod_price,quantityFROMOrderItems,Products,VendorsWHEREProducts.vend_id=Vendors.vend_idANDOrderItems.prod_id=Products.prod_idANDorder_num=20007;
